														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1505161">
									

<p>Fair enough; I'll be the first to admit that it was a somewhat conservative first attempt. Mostly this was an exercise in style, formatting and to explore the idea of &quot;The Destroyers&quot; as something more than an overpowered alien threat.</p>
<p>If I may ask: what did you like? What left you feeling flat? What would you have done differently? I genuinely would like feedback, because I haven't stretched my writing muscles in years, and was wanting to get back into it. I'd actually love some real criticism that I could work from, and I'm comfortable enough in myself that I can handle honest talk.</p>

							</div>

								
					
